---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Apply | YWAM Sendai"
  description="Apply to YWAM Sendai using the unified application form for students, staff, teams, and visitors."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="stack">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Apply to YWAM Sendai</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title max-w-title">
            One application form for students, staff, teams, and visitors.
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="lead">
          YWAM Sendai uses one main application form for several types of applicants.
          The form is designed to route each person into the appropriate process.
        </p>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="#application-form" class="btn-primary">Start Application</a>
          <button type="button" class="btn-secondary-dark open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-secondary-dark">Contact</a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-inverse-soft mb-0">
          Applying is not only administrative. It is also part of discernment, preparation, and communication.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-dark stack-sm">
        <p class="eyebrow">Quick Guide</p>
        <h2 class="card-title">Who this form is for</h2>
        <p>
          This form is used for school applicants, long-term staff applicants,
          short-term teams, and individual visitors or short-term participants.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Students</h3>
          <p>For applicants to YWAM schools such as DTS or DBS.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Long-term staff</h3>
          <p>For those applying to join YWAM Sendai as staff.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Teams</h3>
          <p>For short-term teams seeking to connect or visit.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Visitors</h3>
          <p>For individual visitors or short-term participants.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Before You Apply</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">A few things to keep in mind</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">General eligibility</h3>
          <p>
            Applicants should normally be at least 18 years old, or 17 if they will turn 18
            during their DTS. Functional proficiency in either English or Japanese is also required.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Some roles have prerequisites</h3>
          <p>
            Certain pathways have additional requirements. For example, long-term staff applicants
            must have completed a YWAM Discipleship Training School (DTS).
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">If you are unsure</h3>
          <p>
            If you are not sure whether you should apply as a student, staff member, team, or visitor,
            it is better to contact YWAM Sendai first and clarify your path.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="application-form" class="section bg-paper border-top">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Application Form</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Start here</h2>
        <p class="lead mx-auto">
          Select the category that best matches your situation, and the form will guide you from there.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
        <div
          style="width:100%;min-height:640px;"
          data-fillout-id="2SNM7DhHQKus"
          data-fillout-embed-type="standard"
          data-fillout-inherit-parameters
          data-fillout-dynamic-resize
        ></div>
      </div>

      <div class="container-narrow center" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <p class="text-soft">
          If the embedded form does not load correctly, please contact us and we can help you continue.
        </p>
        <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
          <button type="button" class="btn-secondary open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-text">Contact YWAM Sendai</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="https://server.fillout.com/embed/v1/" defer></script>
</Layout>